	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="auto_name">Gallia</placeName> aliquot iam septimanas nihil certi habeo prater ea, quae in his continentur literis, et quod d. Coignetius ex aula scribit 27. iunii papistas vehementer tumultuari, sed nihilo minus longe et late propagari evangelium.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Uxorem et familiam <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentorati</placeName> relictam revocavit in aulam; antea quoque d. <persName type="auto_name">Roya</persName> relicto <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentorato</placeName> in Galliam rediit.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Metuunt viri prudentes turbas novas, quod nullus sit modus tyrannidis papistarum, <placeName type="auto_name">Parisiensium</placeName> maxime.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vana sunt, quae referuntur de <placeName type="auto_name">Condensi</placeName>, quasi papistarum sequatur religionem.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Verum tamen illud est, quod metu nimio multa impedit, neque ita neglectus et contemptus est in aula, sed inter primos.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non pudet quosdam hoc affirmare pro certo, quod ipsi factum optarent; erras tu forte in nomine; nam Monasteriensem episcopum invasit <persName type="auto_name">Erichus Brunsvicensis</persName>, non Wirtzburgensem, ut ex literis intelliges.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pugnaret cum canonibus et authoritate concilii, si alibi quam Tridenti concluderetur; <foreign xml:lang="de">ich acht aber wol, es stäcke darhinder, das man die execution wunderbarlich ordne, hebe und lege;</foreign> sed vicit agnus de tribu Iuda.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iam nunc celebrantur comitia <placeName type="auto_name">Badae</placeName> inter Bernenses et Sabaudiae principis legatos, et legati, qui <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileae</placeName> fuerunt, Badam redierunt.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid futurm sit, brevi audiemus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Der fürst wil vil;</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bern</placeName> wil wenig; werdent kum zamen kummen.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Claronensis</placeName> causa dilata est in 12. septembris resumenda <placeName type="auto_name">Badae</placeName> a sequestribus.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Man wart, wie es sich schicken wölle zuͦ <placeName type="auto_name">Haveldegras</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vivos voluerunt devorare <persName type="auto_name">Lutherani Bremenses</persName> quoque sed furere desierunt et salvi sunt Bremenses.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="manual"><foreign xml:lang="la">Si <persName type="auto_name">Palatinus</persName> perseverarit</foreign>, werdend sy inn wol blyben lassen.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="manual"><foreign xml:lang="la">Haec causa gubernatur a deo; hic inclinat, quo vult</foreign>, und söltents all wild werden, der... elmaister Brentz wirt ouch zuͦletst an das antthoupt kummen.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gott läpt und ist gerächt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas, quas hic tibi mitto fideliter, probe obsignatas remittes; uteris illis prudenter nec quibusvis communicabis.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quotidie ex <placeName type="auto_name">Gallia</placeName> literas expecto.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quantum me attinet, aegroto iam tres septimanas; coepi hodie redire in sacram cathedram, verum confractis sim viribus et torpor totum occupavit corpus; caput debilitate opprimitur.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed, quod visum est domino, cum hoc constet optimum esse, fiat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non sine difficultate haec scribo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Wie kumpts, das ir so wenig hapt uß <placeName ref="l572" cert="high">Wirtenberg</placeName>? etc.</s>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto">30. iulii.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta fratrem, sororem, nepotes etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus ille.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="29" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosio Blaurero</persName> Lüthmerkae agenti, domino meo colendissimo et fratri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="30" xml:lang="de" type="auto">An m. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosien Blaureren</persName> zuͦ <placeName type="auto_name">Lüthmerken</placeName> im <placeName ref="l774" cert="high">Durgöw</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
